    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The main portion of this set of bagpipes is fashioned from the dried skin of a cauthooj, with the feathers still attached. The bird\u2019s vocal cords are crafted into the instrument\u2019s reeds. The pipes grant a +2 item bonus to Performance checks while playing music with them.",
